# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added

- send() and recv() methods.
- Multishot IO operations.
- Units for command line arguments.
- accept() method.
- [Location and target](/rawstor/librawstor/blob/main/docs/locations_and_targets.md) semantics.
- cancel_all() routine.
- OST backend implementation.

### Removed

- rawstor_empty() method.

## 
